reviews.text:
Tasty n value 
Dun miss it
very delicious
Afternoon tea set are worth for money

First time here. Fine food. Good background music. Sometimes, the aircon is a bit too cold. Noisy at times when workers are cleaning up, which got my body all tensed up. Also, despite the small size of the restaurant, the servers cant see you when you want to order.
Great for lunch. I like the Korean rice cake or stone pot with a milk tea.
